OL,3,CRibena factory worker dies three days
OL,4,Cafter 'serious incident'
OL,6,FA 50-year-old man has died after an
OL,7,Fincident at a factory in which makes
OL,8,Fsoft drinks Ribena and Lucozade.
OL,10,FPolice were called to the factory on
OL,11,FRock Lane, in Coleford, just before
OL,12,F4pm on 22 April, to reports that a
OL,13,Fworker had been injured during a
OL,14,F"workplace incident."
OL,16,FThe man was taken to Southmead
OL,17,FHospital to be treated for serious
OL,18,Finjuries, but died three days later,
OL,19,Fpolice have confirmed.
